  "text": "In summary, these results demonstrate that individual GR box sequences contribute only moderately to viral genome encapsidation, independently of the ratio of capsid to vgRNA present in the cell during particle assembly. This is in line with our previous findings at even higher cellular concentrations of packageable vgRNA [CITATION_1] . Thus, we are unable to reproduce the reported major role of GRI for PFV vgRNA packaging [CITATION_2] .",
